    {
      "id": "VictoryRoad1FRoom2_Text_LetMeGoWithYou",
      "en_US": [
        "...I’m Marley.\n",
        "...You are?\r",
        "Oh... {STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0}, will you help me,\n",
        "please?\r",
        "I want to get through this tunnel.\n",
        "Will you let me go with you?\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "VictoryRoad1FRoom2_Text_DecidedToGoWithMarley",
      "en_US": [
        "{STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0} decided to go with\n",
        "Marley!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "VictoryRoad1FRoom2_Text_IllHealPokemon",
      "en_US": [
        "Marley: ...Pokémon shouldn’t be\n",
        "hurt... I’ll heal them..."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "VictoryRoad1FRoom2_Text_YouTookSoLong",
      "en_US": [
        "Marley: ...You took so long...\n",
        "Please, don’t make me wait...\r",
        "I felt a little forlorn waiting...\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "VictoryRoad1FRoom2_Text_YoureGoingBack",
      "en_US": [
        "Marley: ...You’re going back...\n",
        "Too bad... Bye-bye...\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "VictoryRoad1FRoom2_Text_IAppreciateEscorting",
      "en_US": [
        "Marley: ...Oh! This is it.\n",
        "There’s a stone tablet ahead...\r",
        "I wanted to see the Pokémon that\n",
        "visits it, that’s all...\r",
        "...I appreciate your escorting me...\r",
        "...Just a little...\r"
      ]
    },
